text: Arizona's 11th Legislative District is one of 30 in the state, covers parts of Pima and Pinal counties. As of 2018 there are 61 precincts in the district, 34 in Pima and 27 in Pinal, with a total registered voter population of 135,364. ==Political representation== The district is represented for the 2019-2021 Legislative Session in the State Senate by Vince Leach (R) and in the House of Representatives by Mark Finchem (R) and Bret Roberts (R). ==References== Category:Pima County, Arizona Category:Pinal County, Arizona Category:Arizona legislative districts
title: Arizona's 11th legislative district
